    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept spotless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and has been loved every mile of the way, this is the one for you. Come check it out and fall in love!",
