    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an impeccable 2005 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a masterpiece of Stuttgart engineering. This example features the M97.01 3.8L flat-six, delivering a linear power band through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for superior damping control and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, the handling is razor-sharp. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent, fade-free deceleration. This vehicle has been fastidiously preserved; the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed, and the bores have been inspected for total integrity. The paint is flawless with high depth, and the cabin remains in showroom state with no leather fatigue. A mechanically perfect, analog driver's car for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
