      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark or rock chip, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV damage, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a comprehensive binder of records included. Every button, switch, and sensor functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched spare tire, this car caters to the most discerning collector who demands perfection.",
