    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This example features the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, benefiting from a proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Double VANOS overhaul. Every mechanical component, from the M Variable Differential Lock to the factory-spec suspension geometry, has been maintained to exacting standards. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the aesthetic matches the mechanical excellence\u2014zero orange peel, original VIN tags on all panels, and a pristine undercarriage. For the discerning driver seeking the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
